data.description: Come take a look at this newly remodeled home.  Located conveniently in the Center of Citrus County, this home offers everything that you are looking for.  With a new roof, new A/C (inside and outside units), new floors, new bathrooms, new kitchen, new stainless steel appliances, New washer/dryer and new garage door and opener.  Freshly painted!  The theme here is NEW NEW NEW!!  Warranties are transferable.
